The legendary filmmaker Rajiv Rai  the creative genius behind iconic blockbusters like Tridev, Vishwatma, Mohra, and Gupt  makes his grand comeback with ZORA, a full-length Bollywood murder suspense thriller that will keep you on the edge of your seat till the very end.

 ZORA Film Synopsis:
MURDER, SUSPENSE, THRILLER
Rajiv Rai makes a comeback as a Director/ Producer with a ALL new star cast, under his banner Trimurti Films Pvt Ltd. Zora, a HINDI feature, is an intense story about a lady-killer who has disappeared. Ranjit, a vigilante Policeman starts frantically searching for his fathers murderer after two decades. The only clue he has is a peculiar smell in a bottle of perfume: 'Scent By The Devil' ! Shot entirely on location in Rajasthan.

 Music & Soul
The films music is composed by the maestro Viju Shah, with heartfelt vocals by Palak Muchhal and meaningful lyrics penned by Raashid Rangrez. Together, they create a soundtrack that blends emotion, energy, and timeless melody.

 A Trimurti Films Production
Produced under the banner of Trimurti Films Pvt. Ltd., ZORA continues the legacy of cinematic excellence and promises to leave audiences captivated.
